{"tid":189463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"轉戰挪超好腳頭 N_Ben又有金句","createTime":"2017-04-06T12:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T06:14:07.000Z","uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba049484ca71289a4d0833a7fdfa77414f13748c","tid":189463,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"轉戰挪超好腳頭 Lord賓又有金句<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0f22433d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 體育<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0f22433d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】已過檔洛辛堡的丹麥中鋒賓特拿，在挪超上陣兩仗入兩球，賽後霸氣回答記者提問，表示自己到哪裡，都很享受做自己。<br />\n賓特拿（Nicklas Bendtner）一向語不驚人死不休，自負得來帶點可愛，在球壇有「Lord賓」稱號。近年足球事業停滯不前的他，周三第2次代表洛辛堡出戰挪超，在大勝辛迪夫佐特3:0一役射入1球，開鑼連續兩戰都有入球。賽後，接受挪威電視台女記者訪問時，這位中鋒再次送上金句。 女記者問他：「在挪威做回賓特拿，是否覺得很美妙？」他回答說：「在哪裡做賓特拿都一樣好。」 賓特拿對上一支效力的球隊，是英冠的諾定咸森林，可惜上陣17場僅入兩球，球隊成績亦欠佳，遂在上月決定轉戰挪超，冀在新環境下轉運。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://更多now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9Anow.com&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5637ab93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更多now.com</a>體育新聞及英超、西甲精華，請按此<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾都有新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70bfa2beb75c5a6bacc1616a4423f8a4a7e892e","tid":189463,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"要去挪威呢d第1000000組別聯賽搵存在感"},{"pid":"5b3f145d0f70410c0910b1ac894f0df63af82075","tid":189463,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"賓特拿對上一支效力的球隊，是英冠的諾定咸森林，可惜<span style=\"color: red;\">上陣17場僅入兩球</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/